    • getScoreCalculationType

      private AssignmentType getScoreCalculationType(IAssignable leftAssignable, IAssignable rightAssignable)
      Get the score calculation type for the given assignables depending on this cases:
      1. One of the assignables is fictive, the score calculation needs to use the worst score possible
      2. There is not assignment with the two assignables, the score calculation needs to compute the score
      3. There is already an effective assignment between the two assignables, the score calculation needs to use the best score possible to fix the assignment
      4. There is already an assignment that is forbidden, the score calculation needs to compute the wort score possible
      Parameters:
      leftAssignable - the assignable on the left side of the assignment
      rightAssignable - the assignable on the right side of the assignment
      Returns:
      AssignmentType.FORBIDDEN in case number 1 and 4, AssignmentType.FORCED in case number 2, AssignmentType.COMPUTED in case number 3

    • getAssignablesScore

      private double getAssignablesScore(UniqueAssignableWrapper leftAssignable, UniqueAssignableWrapper rightAssignable)
      Get the score of two assignables and use the left assignable duplications counter to add a score malus.
      Parameters:
      leftAssignable - the assignable on the left side of the assignment
      rightAssignable - the assignable on the right side of the assignment
      Returns:
